{
  "texts": [
    "Baxter et al. [100] developed a general framework for embedding the communication message in the FH-MIMO radar, taking into account different signaling strategies.",
    "Communication-centric ISACCommunication-centric ISAC systems consider information transmission as the primary task, and the implementation of sensing functionality into existing communication systems as a secondary task [13].",
    "In general, the existing communication waveforms can be modified with high design flexibility to achieve the additional sensing capability [101].",
    "For example, the OFDM waveform with the IEEE 802.11p standard has been used by Reichardt et al. [102] for both communication and target sensing in vehicular networks.",
    "To improve the range resolution and speed estimation accuracy, Kumari et al. [103] used the OFDM waveform with IEEE 802.11ad standard for dual services and developed effective algorithms for target detection and parameter estimation."
  ]
}